<div id="banner">
	<h1>Eldred Petition</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Everything is under copyright. But most of those things aren’t making money, so no one cares about their copyright anymore. The Eldred Act will let you use those things.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.petitiononline.com/eldred/petition.html">Sign the petition.</a> Tell your friends.</p>

<p><strong>Update:</strong> Here’s a graph of the number of signatures over time. Each tick is about 80 minutes (the spike is Slashdot, of course):</p>

<p><img src="../2002/eldredActGraph" alt="graph of Eldred signatories over time, going from 300 to 5000" /></p>

